---
title: Thai Inspired Beef and Noodle Stir-Fry with Sugar Snaps and Sesame Seeds
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Thai Inspired Beef and Noodle Stir-Fry in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R13_W09_UK_G11883-13177-4_Main_Low-cb25f020.jpg
